          <p><strong>Why it works:</strong> Simple protein with almost no prep.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>2 eggs</li>
            <li>1 slice toast</li>
            <li>Small side of fruit</li>
            <li>1 teaspoon butter or olive oil</li>
          </ul>
          <ol>
            <li>Cook eggs to your preferred doneness, ensuring they are fully cooked if needed.</li>
            <li>Toast the bread and butter lightly.</li>
            <li>Serve with a side of fruit for color and freshness.</li>
          </ol>
          <div class="highlight">
